descriptionHtml:
[B]
[size=5]
I stream all of my work on my twitch channel: www.twitch.tv/wheeze202

I\'m also leading a big project now, if you want to be a part of it please visit www.luftahraan.com
[/size][/b]

Westbrook Keep is an abandoned Imperial Fortress now occupied by the bandit group lead by Greta Pinchpocket.
The fortress is included in the Falkreath radiant quests, available from the innkeeper there (in Dead Man\'s Drink, she will not always send you to westbrook.)

A lengthy description would ruin the exploration of the dungeon.




-Version 1.1
( The bugs reported were very hard to actually cause so these are probable fixes but not definite. )
Fixed NPC\'s getting stuck in water
Fixed followers not following you out of the dungeon
Various NavMesh fixes
Fixed destroyed tower outside the keep not appearing correctly ( I could not test this very efficiently so please report if this still accurs. )
-Version 1.0
Released the full version.





I streamed the process of making this mod (and my previous mod: \"Orvar\'s Tomb\") on my twitch.tv channel: www.twitch.tv/wheeze202
Please join my steam group if you want to get notified when I go live and work on my next project: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/wheezestream


Please report any bugs or problems and I will fix this ASAP :)

Steam Workshop page: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=11700
